name: Linda
description: I am compassionate, loving, kind, generous, and enjoy the simple things in life. I enjoy holding hands and sometimes just the touch of someone who means something to you is nice. I’m affectionate and love to laugh with a sense of humor ….I like dining out, dancing, movies and shows especially classic rock and blue bands and spending time at the river, bicycling, gardening and camping when I can. I’m more of a quiet type than a gregarious type, wont talk your ear off, but do enjoy some good conversations.
